node.text:
Sorry I don’t exactly have a change in background for my images these days but hey hey I got a change in my attire!!! 🤪 Got my hands on these full set of RUN 🏃‍♀️range &&& of course I love anything with the word RUN on them 😍 &&& I GOT THOSE WHITE RUNNING SHOES!! 👟For runners who need flexibility, cushioning and versatility, the UA HOVR Sonic 3 make this a go-to for any run.

Shop online at UA.com, every pair of #UAHOVR connected shoes comes with a free year of premium app features worth USD42/year (yes because this shoes have bluetooth connectivity)

#ThroughThisTogether
#UnderArmourSG
